title: New Creator: Dan "Vibe" Scherlong
body:
New Creator: Dan "Vibe" Scherlong

Social Handle: https://twitter.com/vibelol https://www.twitch.tv/vibelol
Info: Vibe is a pro player, coach, and variety streamer. Vibe likes to educate his viewers and provides a positive environment for his community to enjoy games.


Targeted Use Case: Dan is interested in having a coin to reward and engage his community and to setup the Discord bot for gated roles on exclusive content, as well as exclusive events and engagements for his fans.


Community Treasury Grant Tier: $500

A "Yes" vote would approve Dan "Vibe" Scherlong as a creator, and provide a $500 grant.

A "No" vote would reject Dan "Vibe" Scherlong from the platform.
author: 0xa8672C3cef0dCe305102f20AC820c921c91fF7e2
